metadata.name: King of the Ashes
metadata.description:
Sometime in our future, an autonomous drone roves the wastelands in search of interesting life and lands to survey. 

The Ai control system sends the collected images to itself in our modern day, as the receivers in its own time have been long offline.

These images come without context or associated data. We're left to draw conclusions based solely on that which we see. 

This is one such image.
